\label{c:main branched} Let $\Gamma$ be a branch. Every automorphism of $\Tt^{M}_\Gamma$ unbounded in $\Gamma$ is conormal in $\Aut(\Tt^{M}_\Gamma)$.
\begin{proof} By \cref{c:semibranch strictly increasing,l:move maximally,f:li2019automorphism}.
\end{proof}

