\label{c:main pointed} Let $\gamma$ be a point. Every automorphism of $\Tt^M_\gamma$ permuting infinitely many cones above $\gamma$ and unbounded below $\gamma$ is conormal in $\Aut(\Tt^{M}_\gamma)$.
